OL,6,FA woman from Oxfordshire who
OL,7,Fdiscovered she had cancer when she was
OL,8,Feight months pregnant says she's lucky
OL,9,Fto be alive.
OL,11,FNikki Penrice had been in hospital
OL,12,Fwith a pregnancy condition that causes
OL,13,Fextreme sickness but when doctors
OL,14,Fcarried out a scan to check her kidney
OL,15,Ffunction they discovered she had bowel
OL,16,Fcancer.
OL,18,F"I just felt numb," she said.
