OL,3,CMum diagnosed with cancer when
OL,4,Cpregnant says she's lucky to be alive
OL,6,F"I didn't really take everything in, I
OL,7,Fwas so focused on getting Connie here
OL,8,Fsafe I kind of put that to the back of
OL,9,Fmy mind and just concentrated on
OL,10,Fgetting Connie here and I thought to
OL,11,Fmyself once Connie's here then I can
OL,12,Ftackle that part of things."
OL,14,FNikki was quickly induced and baby
OL,15,FConnie arrived safely.
OL,17,FHowever, the tumour grew rapidly and
OL,18,Fjust 11 days later, it had perforated
OL,19,Fher bowel.
