OL,3,CMum diagnosed with cancer when
OL,4,Cpregnant says she's lucky to be alive
OL,6,FBut one year later, her dad was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with incurable cancer and
OL,8,Fdied 17 days later.
OL,10,FNow fully recovered, Nikki and her
OL,11,Ffamily are planning to take part in
OL,12,FRace for Life this summer to raise
OL,13,Ffunds for life-saving research by
OL,14,FCancer Research UK.
OL,16,FLeona Potter, Nikki's mum, said: "I
OL,17,Fcan't even begin to tell you how proud
OL,18,FI am of her, how she's dealt with it,
OL,19,Fthe pain, the suffering, she's
OL,20,Famazing."
